[00:57.071]I read your note, and I know just what you want to hear.
[01:10.197]It hurts less over time, but I’m not getting stronger. I just leave pieces behind.
[01:20.417]And I can only fall so many times before I’m broke, unrecognizable.
[02:04.966]Now all I’ve left to give is the piece that still remains, and you bring the pieces back.
[02:22.337]Love, it only reconstructs the pain.
[02:32.189]As time fails to elapse, I’m finding you were everything to me.
[02:45.920]Now my future and my past are ending tragically the same
